Heat a #waffle iron{}. Add @Belgian Waffle{4%unit} to iron. Warm for about ~{30%seconds}.

-- TOASTER OR OVEN ALTERNATIVE: Heat toaster or traditional oven to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about 1 minute. MICROWAVE ALTERNATIVE: Microwave waffle for 20 seconds.

Arrange @French Macarons{1%unit}, waffles, @Lemon Cheesecake{8%ounce}, and @SkinnyDipped Strawberry Lemonade Almonds{3.5%ounce} on a #board{} or #platter{} and serve!

> If you're feeling fancy, arrange the desserts on a #cake stand{} or fine china plates.